---
title: One-Pan Tortelloni Gratin with Kale and Parmesan Breadcrumbs
description: Pasta + pesto + Parmesan cheese: it’s an equation that never fails. Add in a crispy panko breadcrumb topping and now things are really starting to add up. But to really make this dish worth more than the sum of its parts, you gotta add in a powerhouse veggie like kale. It takes this tortelloni bake from creamy and crusty to hale and hearty and incredibly satisfying.
